description:
Most triathletes runners or people who are 18 years and above don't understand why they don't have air?, Why they sink? or why they swim slow.

We learned that if we protect our lower back, loosen our neck we swim much faster with much less effort.

In this course you get 10 different workouts(every workout should be repeated exactly 3 times), more than 30 unique videos, if you practice 3 times a week the course will take you 3 months and if 2 times a week it would take you 2 months.

WEST technique helps thousands of people get their life back,live a healthier and a stress free life and swim much faster.

join us and you will understand why?
title: Swim faster 1000 m & improve your WEST swimming technique
